<h1><i class="fa fa-cloud"></i>Platforms</h1>

<ol class="breadcrumb">
	<li><i class="fa fa-cloud"></i>Platforms</li>
</ol>

<div class="content">
	<p><%= application.name %> is a complete family of self-hostable cloud-based sharing platforms. Each platform has been pre-configured to suit a particular application and set of needs.  This makes it easy for you to get up and running quickly.  There's no need to figure out how to configure the platform.  Just pick the <%= application.name %> that's right for you.</p>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-message"></i>ChatKitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://chatkitty.org">ChatKitty</a> enables you to chat by discussion topic or by direct message so you can keep in touch with your friends, family, or colleagues. Exchange messages, news, files, documents, folders, images, code, music, and more. </p>	
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://chatkitty.org">
						<img class="chats kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/chatkitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption">
						<a href="http://chatkitty.org">ChatKitty</a> - Your Conversations, Your Cloud
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-map"></i>MapKitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://mapkitty.org">MapKitty</a> makes it easy to upload your geolocated images and videos, view them on a map, and share them with others. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://mapkitty.org">
						<img class="maps kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/mapkitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption">
						<a href="http://mapkitty.org">MapKitty</a> - Your Geodata, Your Cloud
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-database"></i>DataKitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://datakitty.org">DataKitty</a> combines the features of <a href="http://filekitty.org">FileKitty</a> and <a href="http://chatkitty.org">ChatKitty</a> together in one platform.  It allows you to share and manage your data and your conversations in one convenient place. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://datakitty.org">
						<img class="data kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/datakitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption">
						<a href="http://datakitty.org">DataKitty</a> - Your Data, Your Cloud
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-image"></i>PhotoKitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://photokitty.org">PhotoKitty</a> is a cloud-based photo management and sharing system that makes it easy to manage, view, backup and share your photos. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://photokitty.org">
						<img class="photos kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/photokitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption">
						<a href="http://photokitty.org">PhotoKitty</a> - Your Photos, Your Cloud
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-code"></i>SourceKitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://sourcekitty.org">SourceKitty</a> allows you to easily upload, manage, and share your source code. It include a code editor with syntax highlighting for most popular programming languages. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://sourcekitty.org">
						<img class="coder kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/sourcekitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption">
						<a href="http://sourcekitty.org">SourceKitty</a> - Your Code, Your Cloud
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-folder"></i>FileKitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://filekitty.org">FileKitty</a> makes it easy for you to upload, manage, and share your files. FileKitty includes viewers for PDF documents, sounds, and videos so you can easily view and share your files. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://filekitty.org">
						<img class="files kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/filekitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption">
						<a href="http://filekitty.org">FileKitty</a> - Your Files, Your Cloud
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-bucket"></i>S3Kitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://s3kitty.org">S3Kitty</a> allows you to use your own S3 buckets with an easy to use web interface.  It combines the capacity of S3 with the familiar look and feel of your desktop or mobile OS. S3Kitty makes S3 easy. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://s3kitty.org">
						<img class="buckets kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/s3kitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption"><a href="http://s3kitty.org">S3Kitty</a> - Your Buckets, Your Cloud</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-video"></i>VideoKitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://videokitty.org">VideoKitty</a> makes it easy for you to upload, manage, and share your videos. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://videokitty.org">
						<img class="video kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/videokitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption"><a href="http://videokitty.org">VideoKitty</a> - Your Videos, Your Cloud</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-moon"></i>DreamKitty</h2>
				<p><a href="http://dreamkitty.org">DreamKitty</a> is a cloud-based AI image generation platform. Using simple text prompts, you can visualize virtually anything that you can think of. Let DreamKitty help to you explore and share your dreams. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://dreamkitty.org">
						<img class="dreams kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/dreamkitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption">
						<a href="http://dreamkitty.org">DreamKitty</a> - Your AI Images, Your Cloud
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<h2><i class="fa fa-music"></i>MusicKitty</h2>
				<p>You love your music. Now you can love the platform that you use to play, manage, and share your music. <a href="http://musickitty.org">MusicKitty</a> lets you run and customize your own music server. </p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-sm-6">
				<div class="figure">
					<a href="http://musickitty.org">
						<img class="audio kitty attention" src="images/logos/clouds/musickitty-cloud-icon.svg" />
					</a>
					<div class="caption">
						<a href="http://musickitty.org">MusicKitty</a> - Your Music, Your Cloud
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>

	<div class="section">
		<h2><i class="fa fa-question-circle"></i>Which <%= application.name %> Is Right For You?</h2>
		<p>To pick the platform that's right for you, just answer these questions: </p>

		<div class="left aligned figure well">
			<ul>
				<li>If you just want to manage your files and don't need the ability to exchange messages, use <a href="http://filekitty.org">FileKitty</a>. </li>
				<li>If you mainly want to communicate with friends, family or colleagues, use <a href="http://chatkitty.org">ChatKitty</a>. </li>
				<li>If you would like to manage and share both files and messages, use <a href="http://datakitty.org">DataKitty</a>. </li>
				<li>If you are a photographer and want to manage and share your photos, use <a href="http://photokitty.org">PhotoKitty</a>. </li>
				<li>If you need to manage geolocated data, like aerial drone photos, use <a href="http://mapkitty.org">MapKitty</a>. </li>
				<li>If you want to manage and play music, podcasts, or audio, use <a href="http://musickitty.org">MusicKitty</a>. </li>
				<li>If you want to manage and play videos, use <a href="http://videokitty.org">VideoKitty</a>. </li>
				<li>If you are a software developer and want to manage your source code, use <a href="http://sourcekitty.org">SourceKitty</a>. </li>
				<li>If you want to experiment with AI generated images, use <a href="http://dreamkitty.org">DreamKitty</a>. </li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>